exhaustive:详尽的 what I tell my patients is to compile an exhaustive list of all the ways that the person was wrong for you.
hint:线索，暗示 when I hear even a hint of idealizing or the faintest whiff of nostalgia in a session
faint:模糊的，虚弱的，微弱的
