nostaligia:怀旧之情，乡愁


brain studies have shown that the withdraw of romantic love activates the same mechanisms in our brain that get activated when addicts are 
withdrawing from substances like cocaine or opioids 停止爱一个人所激发的反应机制和瘾君子戒可卡因或者鸦片所激发的机制一样

the ease with which it gets our mind to do the absolute opposite of what we need in order to recover is remarkable
放下这段感情，我们应该下定决心不受操控，让我们恢复身心，这非常重要
